                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Now I know the "best" grouping arrangements will always be subjective, but still, I have to ask for opinions from some of y'all who have been doing this a lot longer than me. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
A friend and I have recently started playing EQ.  I'm planning to play my chanter (we're still quite low level) and two box a healer (although I'm not sure which type yet..clerics and druids both seem to have advantages).   My friend's not at all sure what she wants to play, except that, like me, she prefers casting classes to pure melee.  Any suggestions as to what would complement an enchanter/healer duo nicely?  Or, for that matter, any suggestions as to what flavour of healer might work out?  One thing we've thought about is a necromancer..very open to suggestions, though.
<br />

<br />
Thanks in advance. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Tassica, Newbie Extraordinaire</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
