                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Play what's most fun for YOU. You will be amazed at what a druid can heal when her player is having fun. You will be amazed at what a paladin can tank when she is having fun. etc =)
<br />

<br />
Druid + Enchanter + Paladin is a solid group. It is fun and versatile. Self-healing tanks make the druid's job MUCH easier.
<br />

<br />
if you find you can't do the things you want to do with your current line up you can always start over and enjoy the lands of Norrath with a new group.
<br />

<br />
If you're not having fun playing the classes you picked, you will not stick around long enough to GET to level 60+</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
