                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Best trio possible is still Warrior/Cleric/Chanter.
<br />

<br />
I know that some folks may disagree with this, but this is the original EQ trinity.  With this group of 3 you can add any other classes you want and you have a great group.
<br />

<br />
Warriors are still the best meat sheilds.  Especially in the high end of the game.  Clerics are the best healers, rezers and have the best HP buffs.  Chanters are the best crowd control and have the best mana regen and haste buffs.
<br />

<br />
The only other trio that comes close is Palladin, Druid, Chanter.  In this team the Palladin has to do the rezzes so you will lose some XP, the druid can't heal as well early on, but adds snares nukes and dots.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: darkred">Iumarex Mistweaver
<br />
Coercer
<br />
Quellious</span></span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
